strings:
<voice_0x01001596><se_high>Carrie: Like, you said you'd be my bodyguards?
Hello? You've been totally useless!
<voice_0x01001597><se_high>Carrie: You can't just accept a job and then go off before you've finished it! But you think that's okay, do you!?

<voice_0x01001599><se_high>Carrie: Ah, that's better!
Okay, I've forgiven you now.
<voice_0x0100159A><se_high>Carrie: Well...good! At least you seem to feel bad about letting me down.
<voice_0x0100159B><se_high>Carrie: I guess I can forgive you. But don't expect to get off so easy next time. You ever pull that kind of trick again, and your butts are toast. Got it?
<voice_0x0100159D><se_def>Cash: Well, two can play at that game.

<voice_0x0100159E><se_def>Cash: I've decided to forget to give you your reward!
I was halfway through getting it for you, WHEN I FORGOT ALL ABOUT IT!
<voice_0x0100159F><se_def>Cash: I mean, come on!? You weren't seriously expecting to get paid after running off halfway through the job, were you!?

<voice_0x010015A0><se_def>Cash: So that's decided, then, I guess.
See ya! Have a nice day! Buh-bye!
